    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-ba08a516-28dc-4664-8899-e912a26237a6">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ba08a516-28dc-4664-8899-e912a26237a6">
                Viscount Hinchingbrooke
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ba08a516-28dc-4664-8899-e912a26237a6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-04-07/debates/0ade3e5a-0282-41c4-9a98-fd90b062bda8/BudgetProposalsAndEconomicSurvey#contribution-ba08a516-28dc-4664-8899-e912a26237a6">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It is very difficult to single out definite items of Government expenditure and say that they should be eliminated. I would rather put it upon an emergency 10 per cent. or 15 per cent. basis, and say that whereas France and Belgium and other countries in Europe have found it necessary, in order to avert inflation, to make percentage cuts, and whereas Britain in 1931 also found it necessary and healthy to make percentage cuts, now is the time to act in a similar manner.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-ba08a516-28dc-4664-8899-e912a26237a6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-04-07/debates/0ade3e5a-0282-41c4-9a98-fd90b062bda8/BudgetProposalsAndEconomicSurvey#contribution-ba08a516-28dc-4664-8899-e912a26237a6">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





